strings: <voice_0x01000AA2><se_high>Accuracy: Now is not the time to argue! Let's go to the beach now!
<voice_0x01000AA3><se_low>*: I'm sorry Jessica, but the water is very dangerous right now...
<voice_0x01000AA4><se_high>Accuracy: Haven't you heard him say he'll think about it?
<voice_0x01000AA5><se_low>*: Sorry Jessica! Hell will take revenge on the Albert family for endangering them.
<voice_0x01000AA6><se_high>Accuracy: People here have half a brain! count
<voice_0x01000AA7><se_high>Accuracy: Let's talk about monsters!
<voice_0x01000AA8><se_high>Accuracy: You are a resident of this tower! Didn't he make you wait in Alexandria?
<voice_0x01000AA9><se_high>Accuracy: I really want to apologize! Anyway, I'm glad I came.
<voice_0x01000AAA><se_high>Accuracy: Hi, I'd like to ask you something, can you come and meet?
<voice_0x01000AAB><se_high>Accuracy: You don't want me to fight sea monsters?
<voice_0x01000AAC><se_low>*: Yes, but... so...
<voice_0x01000AAD><se_high>Accuracy: By the way, do you want to seek help from the big guys?
<voice_0x01000AAE><se_low>*: Hey...Hey...I made it!
<voice_0x01000AAF><se_high>Accuracy: Yes, we are all happy to count on you
<voice_0x01000AC6><se_high>Accuracy: Would you like to try something first? So don't give up and keep on trying!
<voice_0x01000ABC><se_high>Accuracy: Let me know when you're ready, okay? I will wait over there
<voice_0x01000AB9><se_high>Accuracy: This is why it happened! MR Miss. Fourier is done!
<voice_0x01000ABA><se_low>Head of technology: justice
<voice_0x01000AB8><se_high>Accuracy: Are you ready to board the plane?
<voice_0x01000ABB><se_high>Accuracy: Not ready? why are you here Be quick and do what you want!
<voice_0x01000ABC><se_high>Accuracy: Wait here and come back when you are ready.
<voice_0x01000AB0><se_high>Accuracy: Excuse me, did you forget what happened to the tower?
<voice_0x01000AB1><se_high>Accuracy: from the bottom of my heart! ??????? Meaning<:> Doctor Rock! ????????? I recall! Oh, I heard you're going south!
<voice_0x01000AB2><se_high>Accuracy: If a ship is in port, we cannot track it. Do you want to fight this sea monster now?
<voice_0x01000AB3><se_high>Accuracy: I know I can count on you, I haven't forgotten what we saw in the tower.
<voice_0x01000AB4><se_high>Accuracy: Who Is This Dolmach And What Does He Want? for you killed my brother
<voice_0x01000AB5><se_high>Accuracy: I will follow him to the ends of the earth. But before that, you have to secure the sea area so that your ship can sail.
<voice_0x01000AB6><se_high>Accuracy: The sea monsters that stand in our way are very powerful. in order to be better prepared.
<voice_0x01000AB7><se_high>Accuracy: Wait here and come back when you are ready.
<voice_0x01000AC4><se_high>Accuracy: Oh, what's going on? I didn't expect it to be so powerful.
<voice_0x01000AC5><se_high>Accuracy: But in reality it is between us and the mainland to the south. Ready to try again
<voice_0x01000AC6><se_high>Accuracy: Not ready? why are you here Be quick and do what you want!
